xinput-plus (6.6.5-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Remove unused src/emucon.svg (old joystick icon) and its attribution
    file src/emucon-openclipart.org.txt; remove their stanza from
    debian/copyright.
  * i18n: add translations for German (de), Russian (ru), Japanese (ja),
    Chinese Simplified (zh_CN), Chinese Traditional (zh_TW), French (fr),
    Portuguese Brazilian (pt_BR), Italian (it), Polish (pl), Arabic (ar),
    Turkish (tr), and Korean (ko).
  * docs/debian: update pbuilder instructions in compile-and-test-deb.md,
    compilar-y-probar-deb_ES.md, how-to-publish-on-debian.md, and
    como-publicar-en-debian.md to include the orig tarball creation step
    required by the 3.0 (quilt) source format.
  * README.md: add pbuilder build and test section with full command
    sequence and output file locations.
  * ROADMAP.md: mark pbuilder test and smoke-test items as done; document
    exact commands and output paths.

